{"name": "dat1-cli", "metadata": {"name": "dat1-cli", "version": "0.0.4", "classifiers": [], "home_page": null, "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["typer", "inquirer", "boto3", "pyyaml", "yaspin"], "summary": null, "upload_time": 1732737731}, "documentation": ["# dat1-cli\n\nA command line interface for the [dat1](dat1.co) platform.\n\n## Installation\n\n```bash\npip install dat1-cli\n```\n\n\n## Usage\n\nInitialize with your API key:\n\n```bash\ndat1 login\n```\n\nTo initialize a new model project, run in the root directory of your project:\n\n```bash\ndat1 init\n```\n\nTo upload your model to the platform:\n\n```bash\ndat1 deploy\n```\n\nA good starting point for your model is using the [example model](https://github.com/dat1-co/dat1-docker/tree/main/example).\n\nOtherwise, the platform expects a `handler.py` file in the root directory of your project that contains a FastAPI app with two endpoints: GET `/` for healthchecks and POST `/infer` for inference.\nAn example handler is shown below:\n\n```python\nfrom fastapi import Request, FastAPI\nfrom vllm import LLM, SamplingParams\nimport os\n\nllm = LLM(model=os.path.expanduser('./'), load_format=\"safetensors\", enforce_eager=True)\n\napp = FastAPI()\n\n@app.get(\"/\")\nasync def root():\n    return \"OK\"\n\n@app.post(\"/infer\")\nasync def infer(request: Request):\n    request = await request.json()\n    prompts = request[\"prompt\"]\n    sampling_params = SamplingParams(temperature=0.8, top_p=0.95)\n    outputs = llm.generate(prompts, sampling_params)\n    return { \"response\" : outputs[0].outputs[0].text }\n```\n\n## License\n\nMIT\n"], "modules": [{"name": "dat1", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "dat1.__app_name__", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "dat1.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "dat1.ERRORS", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "dat1.app", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "dat1.app.usr_api_key_validate", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "usr_api_key", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "dat1.app.calculate_hashes", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "directory", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "exclude_file_names", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Calculate hashes of files in a given directory, excluding files specified in the exclude list."]}, {"name": "dat1.app.login", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Login and authenticate"]}, {"name": "dat1.app.init", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Initialize the model"]}, {"name": "dat1.app.read_file", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "file_path", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "part_number", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "dat1.app.upload_file_part", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "upload_url", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "file_path", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "part_number", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "dat1.app.upload_file", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "file", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "api_key", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "model_name", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "new_model_version", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "dat1.app.deploy", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "dat1.app._version_callback", "asynchronous": fals